    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean \"the universe has its own plans\"? that sounds like something people say just to cope with how terrifyingly indifferent everything actually is. if we're just a brief flicker, like i said, then any \"peace\" we find is just a temporary distraction from the fact that nothing we do actually persists. it feels like we're just running on a treadmill to nowhere.",
